# UISpringLoadedInteractionEffectState.inactive

**Case**

An interaction state that indicates that spring loading is not engaged.

## Declaration

```swift
case inactive
```

## Discussion

This state has no effect on the styling of the interaction view. It remains in its original style.

## States

- **UISpringLoadedInteractionEffectState.activated**: An interaction state that indicates that the view was spring loaded.
- **UISpringLoadedInteractionEffectState.activating**: An interaction state that indicates that spring loading is about to start.
- **UISpringLoadedInteractionEffectState.possible**: An interaction state that indicates that spring loading is available.
